thread.title: Gary Sheppard
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Gary Sheppard

author: Gary Sheppard
title: Gary Sheppard
text: We tried Omega Rental Cars for the first time in Auckland and everything was perfect from start to finish. The airport pickup was prompt, the girls in reception really friendly and helpful and the car was clean and in good order. Would certainly use Omega again.
